    "reliminary evaluations showed that the system could enerate relevant responses tailored to elderly personas.",
    "(He et al.,) [] Evaluation of CAs handling counseling for people with autism supported by LLMs ChatGPT Public available data from the web-based medical consultation platform DXY [99] This paper selected 100 patient consultation samples related to autism from January 2018 to August 2023.",
    "The questions and responses were anonymized and randomized.",
    "Three chief physicians assessed the responses across four dimensions: relevance, accuracy, usefulness, and empathy, completing 717 evaluations.",
    "The responses were then compared using a Likert scale to gauge their quality."
